\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"df752625338f9545e3f0c85cefe5b2c8d8256c09","tid":1962182,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"笑死 讀書咁自由你都頂唔順<br />\n你真係快啲讓個位比人"},{"pid":"7c78e5e5c4bb59c63085a1924f51a9b977fabbcb","tid":1962182,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eee1517af01fa091b54aae85d9d7ad261ca4bc9","tid":1962182,"uid":345730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲都係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"其實repeat不可恥，利申： re 很多"},{"pid":"3231a1a4b914349ee612cb83c0487a05b2d759c5","tid":1962182,"uid":107666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"讀書都要死？咁將來做野點算？"},{"pid":"62fe1172dd5fe93d6d21269f2c706fbcdae7225a","tid":1962182,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"你太緊張了。放輕些。"},{"pid":"9eb3035c29392d70b3f7cf12cb60b3904be8a1db","tid":1962182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:38:13.000Z","msg":"撐住<br />\n大不了重讀<br />\n只要人在就有希望"},{"pid":"3591ec90cef07e0f17057cd7ef74de7aa230f8ba","tid":1962182,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:52:09.000Z","msg":"加入毅进，实踐抱负"},{"pid":"8225f5fd25f26461231bf65b0ce9f99f93b14d54","tid":1962182,"uid":234081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T20:00:14.000Z","msg":"加油啦 唔好諗得太灰<br />\n有書讀好過無書讀"},{"pid":"e4be94fa816d5be94df7935fb3e2e7e62d0e685e","tid":1962182,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T20:00:50.000Z","msg":"中學定大學？"},{"pid":"ca7a0b1bc08aad6f07d2a8a7f55ca0393f561ff6","tid":1962182,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T20:04:00.000Z","msg":"冇， 最多唔讀， 出嚟做嘢， 做做下又想讀再讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\"